body:
### Arthur Zaczek

> Software is – quite simply – a solid tool, no end in itself.

The experienced windows programmer has one thing in his mind regarding DasZ: to present the client with the ideal solution at all times. His passion for creating top quality software in combination with a degree in Electrical Engineering are important pillars of his effort to fulfill this goal. His patient and likeable nature together with his determination make him a popular partner for all those who take pleasure in high standard software products. He’s living life in the fast lane – at work as well as privately, with his ZZR 1100.

## Contact
